description: The limited edition of Ordinals’ Hard Boiled Keksters features the incomparable trio: Pepsters, Pepeggs, and Pekeks. Each piece exudes character and charm, a must-have for those who value quality and uniqueness. This special release is reserved for our early Kekleberry supporters and chosen Hard Boiled Keksters holders - a testament to our appreciation. This is more than an opportunity, it's a part of an exciting journey of Kekleberry & the Hard Boiled Keksters.
name: Ordinals’ Hard Boiled Keksters: Limited Edition
